@startuml FastBite_Sequencia_CriarEncomenda
title FastBite — Sequencia: Criar Encomenda (Cliente -> Restaurante notificado)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555
  LifeLineBorderColor #888
  ActorBorderColor #555
  ParticipantBorderColor #555
}

actor "Cliente" as Customer
participant "Mobile / Web\n(React Native / React)" as Client
participant "GraphQL API\n(Lighthouse)" as GraphQL
participant "CartService" as CartSvc
participant "OrderService\n#[Transactional]" as OrderSvc
participant "PaymentService" as PaymentSvc
participant "OutboxService" as Outbox
database  "BD (SQLite/MySQL)" as DB
participant "Reverb\n(WebSocket Broker)" as Reverb
participant "Restaurante (Web)" as Restaurant

== 1. Construir carrinho ==

Customer -> Client: adiciona produtos
Client -> GraphQL: mutation addToCart(input)
GraphQL -> CartSvc: addItem(cartId, product, options)
CartSvc -> DB: persist cart_items
CartSvc --> GraphQL: Cart atualizado
GraphQL --> Client: cart total + items

== 2. Checkout ==

Customer -> Client: pressiona "Finalizar Pedido"
Client -> GraphQL: mutation checkout(CheckoutInput)
GraphQL -> OrderSvc: checkout(customerId, paymentMethod, address)

OrderSvc -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION

OrderSvc -> DB: INSERT order (status=PENDING)
OrderSvc -> DB: INSERT order_items + order_item_options
OrderSvc -> DB: INSERT order_address (snapshot)

OrderSvc -> OrderSvc: recordEvent(ORDER_CREATED)
note right
  Persiste OrderEvent +
  enfileira no Outbox
end note
OrderSvc -> DB: INSERT order_events (ORDER_CREATED)
OrderSvc -> Outbox: enqueue('order', id, ORDER_CREATED, payload)

OrderSvc -> PaymentSvc: createPayment(orderId, method, amount)
PaymentSvc -> DB: INSERT payment (status=PENDING)
PaymentSvc -> DB: INSERT payment_events (PAYMENT_CREATED)

alt Pagamento aceite imediatamente (CARD/MBWAY mock)
  PaymentSvc -> DB: UPDATE payment status=COMPLETED
  PaymentSvc -> DB: INSERT payment_events (PAYMENT_COMPLETED)
  OrderSvc -> OrderSvc: transition(CONFIRMED, ORDER_CONFIRMED)
  OrderSvc -> DB: UPDATE order status=CONFIRMED
  OrderSvc -> DB: INSERT order_events (ORDER_CONFIRMED)
  OrderSvc -> Outbox: enqueue('order', id, ORDER_CONFIRMED, payload)
else Pagamento CASH ou pendente
  OrderSvc -> OrderSvc: order fica em PENDING
end

OrderSvc -> DB: COMMIT
OrderSvc --> GraphQL: Order completo
GraphQL --> Client: redireciona para tracking

== 3. Outbox -> Reverb (event-driven) ==

note over Outbox, Reverb #lightyellow
  OutboxEventWorker (background job) faz polling
  e publica os eventos PENDING via Reverb.
end note

Outbox -> Reverb: broadcast DomainEventBroadcasted\nchannels: [\n  customer.{userId}.orders,\n  restaurant.{rId}.orders,\n  order.{id}.tracking\n]

Reverb --> Client: ORDER_CREATED / ORDER_CONFIRMED\n(canal "customer.{id}.orders")
Reverb --> Restaurant: ORDER_CONFIRMED\n(canal "restaurant.{id}.orders")

note over Restaurant #palegreen
  Restaurant Orders Queue
  atualiza em tempo real
  sem polling.
end note

@enduml
